dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the Defense Mapping Agency Hydrographic/Topographic Center. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "From Inter American Geodetic Survey surveys to 1980 and U.S. Navy Surveys to 1983." "U.S. 28053 has been produced in association with the Instituto Geografico Nacional "Tommy Guardia", Panama City, Panama." "Copyright 1995 by the United States Government. No copyright claimed under Title 17 U.S.C." "Soundings in meters." Includes source diagram and tidal information. Map NO.28053 This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
